---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Acceptable Use Policy - Takoyaki Cloud">
  <section class="border-b py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Acceptable Use Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:text-base [&_h2]:font-semibold [&_h2]:text-foreground [&_ul]:space-y-1.5 [&_ul]:pl-4 [&_li]:list-disc">
        <p>This policy governs the use of all services provided by Project Takoyaki Technologies, LLC.</p>

        <h2>Prohibited Activities</h2>
        <p>You may not use our Services to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Send unsolicited bulk email (spam) or operate open mail relays</li>
          <li>Host or distribute malware, viruses, or other malicious software</li>
          <li>Conduct DDoS attacks, port scanning, or unauthorized access attempts</li>
          <li>Host content that infringes on intellectual property rights</li>
          <li>Engage in cryptocurrency mining without prior written approval</li>
          <li>Store or distribute child exploitation material</li>
          <li>Operate services that violate applicable law</li>
          <li>Resell services without prior written agreement</li>
          <li>Disrupt or interfere with other customers' use of the Services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Resource Usage</h2>
        <p>CPU, RAM, and storage are dedicated to your instance. Sustained abuse of shared infrastructure (network, I/O) that impacts others may result in throttling or suspension. We'll contact you before taking action.</p>

        <h2>Network Abuse</h2>
        <p>If your server is the source of DDoS attacks, spam, or other malicious activity, we may null-route or suspend your service. Repeated violations result in termination.</p>

        <h2>Reporting Abuse</h2>
        <p><a href="/contact" class="text-rose-500 hover:text-rose-600">Contact us</a> with IP addresses, timestamps, and logs.</p>

        <h2>Enforcement</h2>
        <p>Violations may result in warning, suspension, or termination depending on severity. We reserve the right to act immediately for severe violations.</p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
